{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"weekOfYear","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The first week of the year is week 1.  This is the week that contains","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the first Thursday of the year.  Equivalently, this is the first week","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that has more than 4 of its days falling within the calendar year."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The value 0 is never returned by this function.  Days contained"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"within a year but occurring before the first ISO 8601 week of that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"year are considered as being contained in the last week of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"previous year.  Similarly, the final days of a calendar year may be"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"considered as being part of the first ISO 8601 week of the next year"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"if 4 or more days of that week are contained within the new year."}]}]}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Returns the ISO 8601 week number for the week containing ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"datetime"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The ISO 8601 week number is the same for every day of the week (from"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Moday through Sunday).  That can produce some unusual resu